"To confirm that you really want to deactivate this account, type in your Matrix user "
"ID:"
msgstr ""
"For å bekrefte at du ønsker å deaktivere kontoen, skriv inn Matrix-brukernavnet ditt:"

#: src/account_settings/general_page/deactivate_account_subpage.rs:156
